Instructions below for non-steam activation:
Step 1: Click Here
Step 2: Enter the 16-digit Product Redeem Code provided.
Step 3: If you’re not already signed in to Telltale Games, you will need to log in or register for a Telltale Games account.
Step 4: The game you are redeeming can be downloaded immediately and is now linked to your account.
Step 5: Just log in to this account any time to access the game you just activated.
Step 6: You may need to enter your Telltale account e-mail and password to unlock the game the first time you play.
Step 7: Your collection of games can always be accessed and downloaded from your My Games section, which is located in your user profile drop down menu.
